{"tid":1211504,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"用iphone者務必清history","createTime":"2019-06-12T15:53:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T16:03:32.000Z","uid":164920,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d4e3ec7e59f6bcc4dfdeff931804edbc7c127c49","tid":1211504,"uid":164920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:53:41.000Z","msg":"Iphone會記低你出現過係咩地方，所以呢兩日有出去嘅人記得去清History，外國有Law enforcement authorities 會用呢個Location history去做你在場證據，唔知香港狗仔會唔會都咁玩，但都要識清history自保:<br />\nSettings &gt; Privacy &gt; Location Services &gt; System Services (located at the bottom) &gt; Frequent Locations &gt; Significant Location&gt; Clear History<br />\n<br />\n另外提醒大家清Whatsapp入面有提及朋友行蹤嘅message<br />\n<br />\n*大原則係提大家唔好係手機留不利自己或者在場朋友嘅Data<br />\n<br />\n請廣傳"},{"pid":"33d7e90b9d3b5420dbfd07fcf66f46b00bd0661c","tid":1211504,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:55:49.000Z","msg":"Iphone咁危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用華為算"},{"pid":"a6eaf972249d53ce9ab6ee5ff1c2abf56fd5f04b","tid":1211504,"uid":116823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:02:46.000Z","msg":"On9<br />\nApple連美國政府都唔比面<br />\n點會show d on狗"},{"pid":"434c99474c0cf06c91b2363a3083386dbaab41c7","tid":1211504,"uid":116823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:03:32.000Z","msg":"此po已完，請上一頁"}]}